    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The Emergency Hammer is a tool every driver should have! It is designed to help prevent being trapped in a wrecked or submerged vehicle. Should the doors become jammed shut or a seat belt locked after an accident, the double-sided steel hammer points allow the driver to easily shatter side and rear windows, while a safeguarded razor blade cuts easily through safety belts for a quick escape. This emergency hammer includes a black mounting bracket for quick access installation to a roof, dash, or console. The bright orange plastic body make the hammer easy to find and a glow-in-the-dark pin helps spotting in the dark or murky water easier.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Large Universal Car Emergency Hammer Window Punch Seat Belt Cutter Tool 2pk 4pk</h2>\n  <p>The Emergency Hammer is a tool every driver should have! It is designed to help prevent being trapped in a wrecked or submerged vehicle.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>THOUGHTFUL CONSTRUCTION - Dual-Sided Hardened Steel Impact Points Shatters Car Windows in Emergency Situations</li>\n    <li>MULTIPLE EMERGENCY FUNCTIONS - Safeguarded Razor Blade Cuts Trough Seat Belts to Help Free You and Your Passengers</li>\n    <li>HI VISIBILITY &amp; ACCESSIBILITY - Black Mounting Bracket to Keep Hammer In Reach &amp; Glow-in-the-Dark Button For Easy Spotting in the Dark</li>\n    <li>MADE TO WITHSTAND AN IMPACT - Durable, Bright Orange Plastic Body</li>\n    <li>PERFECT STOCKING STUFFER - This compact emergency hammer makes a perfect gift for teens, friends, and loved ones.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/Tools/EH430_emergency_hammer_LG_2pk.jpg\" alt=\"The Emergency Hammer is a tool every driver should have\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASRF-LG</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058488268</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Orange</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Should the doors become jammed shut or a seat belt locked after an accident, the double-sided steel hammer points allow the driver to easily shatter side and rear windows, while a safeguarded razor blade cuts easily through safety belts for a quick escape.</p>\n  <p>This emergency hammer includes a black mounting bracket for quick access installation to a roof, dash, or console. The bright orange plastic body make the hammer easy to find and a glow-in-the-dark pin helps spotting in the dark or murky water easier.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
